							<h2 class="">About Us</h2>
							<h6 class="mb-2">“There is no love sincerer than the love of food.”- George Bernard Shaw, Man and Superman. "</h6>
							<p>The beautiful city-state of Singapore is a grand mix of cultures, destinations, ethnicities, languages, and cuisines. And when it comes to cuisines, the North Indian delicacies have their own set of connoisseurs, which is large and diverse.</p>
							<p>
							    At Pepper Castle, we offer such food connoisseurs the very best of North Indian cuisine that is healthy, tasty, and free from additives. We began our journey in 2012 as a food establishment offering delicious dishes such as Biryani, Pulao, and Kebab, among others. Over the years, we have come to be known as a culinary destination that serves authentic and healthy North Indian fare in Singapore.
							</p>
							<p>
							    The dishes at our restaurant do not contain MSG and added colouring while being halaal-friendly at the same time. At Pepper Castle, allow your taste buds to relish succulent kebabs, tandoori (clay oven based) dishes, a wide variety of Indian breads, vegetable and rice entrees, among many others.
							</p>
